{{Otheruses|Epsilon}}
'''Sector Epsilon''' was the newest sector of the strange [[Space station/Legends|space station]] called [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']]. It was reserved for newcomers to the station and offered several good spots for thos who wished to settle there. There was a small [[connection charge]] to be paid, though, and a quarterly payment was also required for maintenance, communications, power and life support.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

Among the more mysterious settlers in this area were the [[Kalai]] who resided in the [[Destiny (Zirtran's Anchor)|''Destiny'']]. While no pure Kalai were seen roaming the station, their offspring, called the [[lethagoe]]s would venture into the station from time to time.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

